<l>varukamaṟ koṇka ṉorunāṭ parukuvaṉ</l>
<l>paitaṉōy yellām keṭa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May my husband return some day and then will I enjoy (him) so as to destroy all this agonizing sorrow.</l>
